# No "magic" automation

- Prefer minimal, reviewable diffs.
- Avoid drive-by formatting, mass renames, and sweeping rewrites unless the user explicitly asks.
- Do not propose code generation outputs (or changes to generated files) unless explicitly asked.

## When touching formatting

- Only include formatting changes when they are required for correctness or to satisfy an agreed rule.
- If formatting is necessary, keep it scoped to the smallest possible area.
